weka.clusterers

Class AntGridClusterer.Cluster

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.clusterers.AntGridClusterer.Cluster
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<AntGridClusterer.InstancePlaceholder>
    Enclosing class:
    AntGridClusterer

    protected class AntGridClusterer.Cluster
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<AntGridClusterer.InstancePlaceholder>
    This is the cluster that can be assigned to the AntGridClusterer.InstancePlaceholder objects.

    It must not perform actions by itself, but is only used by other classes.

      • centroidUpToDate

        protected boolean centroidUpToDate
        Indicates if the centroid is up to date. As calculating the centroid is costly, but it only changes on member changes, it is worth to track its up to date status.
